Shouldn't have teamed up with
that idiot Kwon Jong Uk...

270
00:33:19,726 --> 00:33:23,552
Yeah, a lot's probably going through your head.

271
00:33:24,441 --> 00:33:27,173
But hey, you're wrong.

272
00:33:27,173 --> 00:33:30,537
It's not any of that.

273
00:33:30,537 --> 00:33:35,666
The worst decision you ever made
was marrying Chu Sang Ah.

274
00:33:35,666 --> 00:33:40,453
The best one I ever made was
marrying Kwon Se Myeong.

275
00:33:41,796 --> 00:33:44,929
Now do you get it?

276
00:33:58,289 --> 00:34:01,335
This is your last chance.

277
00:34:01,335 --> 00:34:04,361
Your call.

278
00:35:29,869 --> 00:35:33,541
Let's die together

279
00:35:37,469 --> 00:35:40,102
tonight.

280
00:35:46,459 --> 00:35:49,432
Have you lost your mind?

281
00:35:50,332 --> 00:35:54,365
It's not fair dying alone.

282
00:35:54,365 --> 00:35:58,558
But before that, let me ask you one thing.

283
00:35:58,558 --> 00:36:02,518
Why go this far?

284
00:36:05,251 --> 00:36:07,724
Sang Ah...

285
00:36:08,411 --> 00:36:14,391
Why are you so set on dragging her
all the way down?

286
00:36:18,430 --> 00:36:22,923
Because that's all you have left.

287
00:36:23,608 --> 00:36:26,775
Out of everything you have,

288
00:36:26,775 --> 00:36:30,915
that's the only thing worth anything.

289
00:36:32,181 --> 00:36:34,508
Damn it.

290
00:36:38,584 --> 00:36:41,850
You think this is rock bottom?

291
00:36:41,850 --> 00:36:44,850
You think this is the end?

292
00:36:44,850 --> 00:36:47,797
Don't be ridiculous.

293
00:36:51,002 --> 00:36:52,806
You want to die?

294
00:36:52,806 --> 00:36:55,231
You really think you can go through with it?

295
00:36:55,231 --> 00:36:57,826
After humiliating yourself?

296
00:36:57,826 --> 00:37:01,179
I know exactly who you are.

297
00:37:01,852 --> 00:37:07,106
You knew this was your last shot
when you walked in.

298
00:37:08,358 --> 00:37:12,111
So think it through.

299
00:37:12,111 --> 00:37:16,578
What you do right now decides everything.

300
00:37:16,578 --> 00:37:20,291
Your life. And Chu Sang Ah's.

301
00:37:20,291 --> 00:37:22,864
Got it?

302
00:39:10,653 --> 00:39:13,244
It's Chu Sang Ah. She's coming out!

303
00:39:13,244 --> 00:39:15,377
How did we...

304
00:39:15,377 --> 00:39:19,037
end up as monsters?

305
00:39:21,385 --> 00:39:24,078
Bang Tae Seop...

306
00:39:24,078 --> 00:39:25,868
I'm not letting it end like this.

307
00:39:25,868 --> 00:39:28,048
Could you comment on the controversy?

308
00:39:28,048 --> 00:39:32,092
I'll use every means
I have to bring Lee Yang Mi down.

309
00:39:32,092 --> 00:39:33,697
Just one statement, please.

310
00:39:33,697 --> 00:39:35,768
I'll take back everything you lost,

311
00:39:35,768 --> 00:39:40,341
and everything that was taken from me.

312
00:39:46,988 --> 00:39:49,987
- Chu Sang Ah!
- Wait!

313
00:39:53,032 --> 00:39:54,231
Chu Sang Ah!

314
00:39:54,231 --> 00:39:55,312
Just a moment!

315
00:39:55,312 --> 00:39:58,087
Sang Ah!

316
00:40:06,619 --> 00:40:09,405
You're just like me.

317
00:40:09,405 --> 00:40:12,877
We're the same kind.

318
00:40:12,877 --> 00:40:16,631
I know exactly

319
00:40:16,631 --> 00:40:19,944
what you're capable of.

320
00:40:22,306 --> 00:40:25,059
You do it your way.

321
00:40:25,059 --> 00:40:28,667
I will do it my way.

322
00:40:28,667 --> 00:40:29,795
[You do it your way, I will do it my way]

323
00:40:29,795 --> 00:40:34,395
Let's see this through.
Each of us, to the end we want.

324
00:41:42,561 --> 00:41:45,158
This is the ancestral grave of Gu Hong Seo,

325
00:41:45,158 --> 00:41:47,903
Son Guk Won's only real rival.

326
00:41:47,903 --> 00:41:49,927
Your task is

327
00:41:49,927 --> 00:41:53,764
to cut off that family line for good.

328
00:41:53,764 --> 00:41:58,789
This is no different from
putting a hit on the dead...

329
00:41:58,789 --> 00:42:04,376
so you have to drive it straight
into the skull and the heart.

330
00:42:04,376 --> 00:42:06,840
That's the only way to end it.

331
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,790
But

332
00:42:08,790 --> 00:42:11,889
you'd be going against
the natural order of life and death.

333
00:42:11,889 --> 00:42:16,562
Whoever does it will have to pay a price.

334
00:42:17,428 --> 00:42:20,868
For example...

335
00:42:21,641 --> 00:42:27,094
someone closest to you might take the hit.

336
00:43:53,442 --> 00:43:58,534
[Missed Call]
[Chu Sang Ah]

337
00:44:23,205 --> 00:44:26,080
[To: Bang Tae Seop,
701, 27-9 Gachan 1-dong, Dongnam-gu, Seoam-si]

338
00:44:32,507 --> 00:44:35,613
What are you doing?

339
00:44:55,868 --> 00:44:57,945
Is this what you got for humiliating yourself?

340
00:44:57,945 --> 00:45:00,488
Watch your mouth.

341
00:45:02,777 --> 00:45:07,730
I'm giving you this for everything
we've been through.

342
00:45:08,705 --> 00:45:11,638
I'm leaving.

343
00:45:12,472 --> 00:45:15,192
Don't come looking for me.

344
00:45:18,348 --> 00:45:21,378
You messing with me right now?

345
00:45:21,378 --> 00:45:24,698
Do you know what I've done for you?

346
00:45:24,698 --> 00:45:26,543
You think I'll take this and just walk away?

347
00:45:26,543 --> 00:45:30,104
Stop doing this kind of shit

348
00:45:31,004 --> 00:45:34,557
and start living like a decent person.

349
00:45:34,557 --> 00:45:37,161
I'm also starting over

350
00:45:37,161 --> 00:45:40,554
somewhere no one knows me.

351
00:45:49,288 --> 00:45:51,570
What, you think you're somebody now

352
00:45:51,570 --> 00:45:55,423
because you've been hanging around Chu Sang Ah?

353
00:45:56,720 --> 00:45:59,692
Don't bullshit me.

354
00:46:13,433 --> 00:46:16,332
Woo Sik...

355
00:46:49,377 --> 00:46:52,403
Where are you going?

356
00:47:01,544 --> 00:47:04,344
Running away?

357
00:47:38,258 --> 00:47:43,844
You're the only proof left
that Lee Yang Mi did this to me.

358
00:47:43,844 --> 00:47:47,283
And you're just going to walk away like this?

359
00:47:48,018 --> 00:47:51,916
Yeah, maybe your life got messed up
because of me and Bang Tae Seop,

360
00:47:51,916 --> 00:47:56,334
but if you run now just to save yourself,

361
00:47:56,334 --> 00:47:59,281
I'm done.

362
00:48:09,789 --> 00:48:12,187
You came here knowing everything, so go ahead.

363
00:48:12,187 --> 00:48:14,913
Make your excuses.

364
00:48:27,766 --> 00:48:31,292
There's nothing to explain.

365
00:48:33,111 --> 00:48:37,105
You just got unlucky...

366
00:48:37,105 --> 00:48:40,695
meeting someone like me.

367
00:48:40,695 --> 00:48:43,855
That's what ruined your life.

368
00:48:51,068 --> 00:48:54,974
You didn't know I was this kind of person?

369
00:48:57,188 --> 00:49:01,908
I've had blood on my hands
just trying to survive,

370
00:49:02,857 --> 00:49:07,424
spent my whole life screwing people over.

371
00:49:11,420 --> 00:49:15,680
And you thought there was something real in me?

372
00:49:22,034 --> 00:49:24,580
Maybe.

373
00:49:25,701 --> 00:49:28,460
But I meant it.

374
00:49:30,630 --> 00:49:33,430
Even if

375
00:49:34,015 --> 00:49:37,368
it was just for a moment.

376
00:49:44,212 --> 00:49:47,545
One last favor.

377
00:49:48,772 --> 00:49:53,799
I'm going to use everything
I have to take Lee Yang Mi down.

378
00:49:53,799 --> 00:49:55,936
So everything you saw,

379
00:49:55,936 --> 00:49:59,811
everything you heard, everything you know.

380
00:49:59,811 --> 00:50:05,017
Anything I can use to go after her,
lay it all out.

381
00:50:15,602 --> 00:50:18,402
You and me...

382
00:50:19,353 --> 00:50:22,526
if we go any further,

383
00:50:23,719 --> 00:50:27,279
it won't just end with us getting hurt.

384
00:50:33,106 --> 00:50:36,892
So stop. Right here.

385
00:51:13,935 --> 00:51:15,445
Did I

386
00:51:15,445 --> 00:51:18,419
really want you dead?

387
00:51:18,419 --> 00:51:21,449
I'm already dead anyway.

388
00:51:21,449 --> 00:51:24,906
When Ji Soo died like that,
something in me died too.

389
00:51:24,906 --> 00:51:28,282
Living like this...

390
00:51:28,282 --> 00:51:31,313
it's no different from being dead.

391
00:51:31,313 --> 00:51:36,773
So even if I break,
I'm taking her down with me.

392
00:51:37,871 --> 00:51:40,053
Please...

393
00:51:40,053 --> 00:51:43,793
Just stop. Please!

394
00:51:46,449 --> 00:51:48,795
Please.

395
00:52:18,191 --> 00:52:20,837
Yeah.

396
00:52:21,517 --> 00:52:24,823
We've become monsters.

397
00:52:26,024 --> 00:52:28,676
- Oh, no!
- No!

398
00:52:32,311 --> 00:52:34,871
Jeong Won...

399
00:52:49,734 --> 00:52:52,121
Go after him.

400
00:52:56,557 --> 00:52:58,917
Jeong Won...

401
00:52:58,917 --> 00:53:01,983
Jeong Won... look at me.

402
00:53:03,690 --> 00:53:06,230
What do I do?

403
00:53:11,417 --> 00:53:14,198
Wait...

404
00:53:14,198 --> 00:53:16,364
Jeong Won!

405
00:53:16,364 --> 00:53:18,781
Look at me.

406
00:53:18,781 --> 00:53:21,867
Stay with me...

407
00:53:23,268 --> 00:53:25,921
Please, stay with me.

408
00:53:25,921 --> 00:53:28,521
Jeong Won...

409
00:53:34,714 --> 00:53:37,701
Please stay with me.

410
00:53:38,861 --> 00:53:40,398
Please...

411
00:53:40,398 --> 00:53:42,754
Jeong Won...

412
00:53:47,581 --> 00:53:49,467
Jeong Won.

413
00:53:49,467 --> 00:53:51,713
Hey...

414
00:53:56,025 --> 00:53:57,776
Jeong Won.

415
00:53:57,776 --> 00:54:00,156
Please.

416
00:54:52,835 --> 00:54:54,349
[Sang Ah]

417
00:54:56,423 --> 00:55:00,159
The number you have dialed is
currently unavailable...

418
00:55:08,864 --> 00:55:12,190
Sir, are you Chu Sang Ah's husband?

419
00:55:13,477 --> 00:55:14,982
Yes...

420
00:55:14,982 --> 00:55:17,765
what is it?

421
00:55:17,765 --> 00:55:19,355
So

422
00:55:19,355 --> 00:55:23,812
you're saying a man in his 30s,

423
00:55:23,812 --> 00:55:28,544
wearing a black top,
stabbed Hwang Jeong Won and fled.

424
00:55:33,352 --> 00:55:37,272
You didn't get a clear look at his face?

425
00:57:21,794 --> 00:57:26,507
Disappointed it wasn't me?

426
00:57:39,256 --> 00:57:40,507
It wasn't me, damn it!

427
00:57:40,507 --> 00:57:42,096
- Hey, keep it down.
- Let go!

428
00:57:42,096 --> 00:57:44,539
- It wasn't me! I didn't do it!
- Be quiet!

429
00:57:44,539 --> 00:57:45,965
- Quiet.
- Hey!

430
00:57:45,965 --> 00:57:47,790
You know it wasn't me. You saw it.

431
00:57:47,790 --> 00:57:49,658
- Shut it. Move.
- You saw it!

432
00:57:49,658 --> 00:57:51,932
- Move.
- Hey! Chu Sang Ah!

433
00:57:51,932 --> 00:57:53,722
You saw I didn't stab her!

434
00:57:53,722 --> 00:57:56,602
Hey! Chu Sang Ah!

435
00:58:00,945 --> 00:58:03,600
What are you going to do now?

436
00:58:03,600 --> 00:58:05,297
It's not him.

437
00:58:05,297 --> 00:58:08,360
I know it.

438
00:58:08,360 --> 00:58:10,456
So what?

439
00:58:10,456 --> 00:58:14,156
You think stepping in now helps you?

440
00:58:17,316 --> 00:58:20,750
Don't get dragged into anything else.

441
00:58:20,750 --> 00:58:23,603
This is as far as it goes.

442
00:58:35,454 --> 00:58:39,488
A rookie actress, identified as Hwang,
has been killed by a stalker.

443
00:58:39,488 --> 00:58:43,881
Nine years ago, she was charged with
attempted murder of her mother's partner,

444
00:58:43,881 --> 00:58:48,305
and is believed to have concealed her past
to pursue an acting career.

445
00:58:48,305 --> 00:58:50,002
The suspect was arrested at the scene.

446
00:58:50,002 --> 00:58:53,015
He had been stalking her since last year

447
00:58:53,015 --> 00:58:54,506
and has multiple prior convictions
for violence,

448
00:58:54,506 --> 00:58:57,532
[Ms. Hwang brutally killed after fight with ex]
including several arrests.

449
00:58:57,532 --> 00:59:01,216
Meanwhile, based on the bundles of
cash found in a bag in the car,

450
00:59:01,216 --> 00:59:04,419
police are not ruling out the possibility that

451
00:59:04,419 --> 00:59:07,876
this was a contract killing,
not just a stalking crime.

452
00:59:07,876 --> 00:59:12,250
[The media covered it all up. Right?
Acting while hiding a murder conviction...]

453
00:59:12,250 --> 00:59:16,209
[The agency casts a convicted murderer
as the lead? Oh my]

454
00:59:16,209 --> 00:59:18,410
[Why do people like this keep showing up?]

455
00:59:33,365 --> 00:59:36,763
[Hwang Jeong Won, 26, deceased]

456
01:00:18,696 --> 01:00:21,002
Darn it.

457
01:00:32,308 --> 01:00:34,395
Excuse me.

458
01:00:34,395 --> 01:00:37,385
What is your relationship to the deceased?

459
01:00:37,385 --> 01:00:39,892
Why?

460
01:00:39,892 --> 01:00:44,445
If there's no next of kin,
she'll be listed as unclaimed.

461
01:00:47,776 --> 01:00:50,240
I'm her next of kin.

462
01:00:50,240 --> 01:00:54,440
Then please sign here.

463
01:01:00,784 --> 01:01:06,776
[Relationship to the deceased: Next of kin]

464
01:01:41,729 --> 01:01:44,463
[Resident Registration Card, Hwang Jeong Won]

465
01:02:06,375 --> 01:02:09,754
[To: Bang Tae Seop,
701, 27-9 Gachan 1-dong, Dongnam-gu, Seoam-si]

466
01:02:09,754 --> 01:02:13,487
What's got you so confident...

467
01:02:18,051 --> 01:02:21,264
You've got something, don't you?

468
01:02:27,673 --> 01:02:33,139
Remember when I worked under Bang Tae Seop
as a mole for the prosecution?

469
01:02:41,802 --> 01:02:45,209
If I spill what I've got,

470
01:02:47,732 --> 01:02:51,299
we all go down together.

471
01:03:06,014 --> 01:03:10,694
Kill Hwang Jeong Won.

472
01:03:20,250 --> 01:03:23,716
[Dark web screenshot of Choi Ji Ho]

473
01:04:24,343 --> 01:04:28,522
This is the USB Hwang Jeong Won sent
before she died.

474
01:04:41,882 --> 01:04:45,554
It has CCTV footage of the man
who killed Park Jae Sang,

475
01:04:45,554 --> 01:04:50,390
and call records between the person
who ordered it and the broker.

476
01:04:50,390 --> 01:04:51,884
[Call Records]

477
01:04:55,512 --> 01:04:59,299
Is this blackmail, or loyalty?

478
01:04:59,299 --> 01:05:02,405
What does it look like to you?

479
01:05:04,254 --> 01:05:06,661
Well...

480
01:05:06,661 --> 01:05:09,911
Either way, it's not hard evidence.

481
01:05:09,911 --> 01:05:11,821
Well...

482
01:05:11,821 --> 01:05:14,028
It'll definitely get an investigation moving,

483
01:05:14,028 --> 01:05:18,101
and it'll be a headache for you.

484
01:05:19,485 --> 01:05:21,389
So

485
01:05:21,389 --> 01:05:25,695
besides getting into Son Guk Won's camp,
what else do you want?

486
01:05:27,095 --> 01:05:30,252
Clean up the leaked video.

487
01:05:30,252 --> 01:05:34,925
And get Sang Ah's film released.

488
01:05:42,365 --> 01:05:44,716
That's almost touching.

489
01:05:44,716 --> 01:05:46,741
After everything,

490
01:05:46,741 --> 01:05:50,246
you still have feelings for her?

491
01:05:50,920 --> 01:05:57,306
Until I make it to the Blue House,
my trophy needs to stay spotless.

492
01:06:02,709 --> 01:06:06,321
This is why I took you in.

493
01:06:27,997 --> 01:06:30,797
You really are

494
01:06:32,351 --> 01:06:35,817
a filthy bastard.

495
01:06:39,040 --> 01:06:41,840
You don't actually believe

496
01:06:42,658 --> 01:06:46,706
there's such a thing as a decent man,

497
01:06:46,706 --> 01:06:49,773
do you?

498
01:07:43,935 --> 01:07:46,646
You're risking all that for what?

499
01:07:46,646 --> 01:07:48,670
I'm cutting Lee Yang Mi loose.

500
01:07:48,670 --> 01:07:50,267
What if I jerk the wheel?

501
01:07:50,267 --> 01:07:53,326
You're going over the edge.
It's only a matter of time.

502
01:07:53,326 --> 01:07:56,129
Medical malpractice. Soliciting murder.

503
01:07:56,129 --> 01:07:59,389
It'll be the most shocking story of the year.

504
01:07:59,389 --> 01:08:00,779
You didn't leave anything behind, huh?

505
01:08:00,779 --> 01:08:02,453
Make it look like suicide.

506
01:08:02,453 --> 01:08:05,750
I'll turn WR to dust.

507
01:08:05,750 --> 01:08:08,694
The real owner of WR

508
01:08:08,694 --> 01:08:11,767
is about to change.
